0:

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: flash blue tag
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Blutag Flash is a line of wearables. Use this skill to purchase products, hear about our policies and ask for our current promotions. 

To open this skill say "Alexa, open flash blue tag"

Once inside the skill, you can say 
- Find me a jacket
- What is your shipping policy
